{"tid":35706,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"菲臘佬：卡利奧斯最好收聲！","createTime":"2016-12-12T09:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T11:25:45.000Z","uid":15745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fca81a69b0272f46b71795357091fe6d7fa5739b","tid":35706,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:03:57.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=DcPKwM4bdEByzsU2II6dPgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=783c25db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦周日再度失分，只能2:2逼和韋斯咸，門將卡利奧斯繼續受盡千夫所指，今次就輪到菲臘尼維利，批評他與其作口舌之爭，倒不如閉嘴專心訓練。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦門將卡利奧斯（Lorius Karius）上輪英超犯錯，導致球隊以3:4遭般尼茅夫反勝，現為球評家的加利尼維利賽後抨擊卡利奧斯，指他令己隊後衛變得焦慮，縱使後者隨即開腔還擊，惟他今輪對韋斯咸表現仍未有改善，連失兩球，領隊高普也承認兩球失球均可避免，使卡利奧斯責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n今仗之後，就輪到菲臘尼維利向卡利奧斯開火，他批評這名23歲德國門將的表現，苛責後者應該「閉嘴」，集中精神訓練自己，而不是對外放話，為自己犯下的過錯辯護。批評卡利奧斯的名宿，不止是加利佬和菲臘佬，利物浦名宿加歷查也參一把腳，他在其節目中「教導」卡利奧斯：「閉嘴！做好你的工作！」<br />\n<br />\n卡利奧斯剛登陸英超就飽服批評，幸而高普仍對他投下信心的一票，能否報答領隊的賞識，就要看卡利奧斯自己的造化了。<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp16801542001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp16801542001&d=DcPKwM4bdEByzsU2II6dPgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=f3660b0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp16801542001&h=28a326d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp16801542001</a>"},{"pid":"f450c3bc2a2beee9fe43783a3ef96aacdacdf0a4","tid":35706,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱"},{"pid":"e68b84f23fe5f08d27a3d7aca3dff6f3954e2108","tid":35706,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da66bda05af97e31943d56a2b82c8ea844ff67e","tid":35706,"uid